    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ON HOLD</h2>Unfortunately, due to a myriad of external factors, we have had to put Forging Glory on hold for the time being in favor of smaller titles.<br><br>It's been an amazing, and painstaking, five year journey.  We've learned a lot and experienced wonderful memories we'll cherish forever.  We hope you will continue to join us in our game development adventure by joining us in playing our smaller titles.<br><br>Again, apologies, and thank you all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/baed5885b146ff8ad741709e7c588bc7.poster.avif?t=1633191366\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/baed5885b146ff8ad741709e7c588bc7.webm?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/baed5885b146ff8ad741709e7c588bc7.mp4?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KICKASSERY</h2>Decapitate, dismember, shatter, and mutilate avatars built of light! You're a God of the arena, annihilating all who challenge you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/7f7821e516134cd42957d7745d0a347a.poster.avif?t=1633191366\" width=480 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/7f7821e516134cd42957d7745d0a347a.webm?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/7f7821e516134cd42957d7745d0a347a.mp4?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTERY</h2>Combat is all about skill in Forging Glory.  You must aim your attacks, and your blocks.  There is no magic &quot;block all&quot; button!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/b8f30b5aa387c25c2ea448d893136d53.poster.avif?t=1633191366\" width=480 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/b8f30b5aa387c25c2ea448d893136d53.webm?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/b8f30b5aa387c25c2ea448d893136d53.mp4?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION</h2>Create the perfect avatars to fit each battle and play-style using limitless weapons and items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/932bf429aba3d004e356ae3cdf4e289a.avif?t=1633191366\" width=620 height=226 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FANDOM</h2>Earn glory by pleasing the crowd, leading you to greater rewards and fame!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/33514e4706eda4f0e3503e0508f32e47.poster.avif?t=1633191366\" width=800 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/33514e4706eda4f0e3503e0508f32e47.webm?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/33514e4706eda4f0e3503e0508f32e47.mp4?t=1633191366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player and multiplayer dynamic campaigns, with 6 game modes.<br></li><li>Fully customizable classless character system<br></li><li>Physics-based combat with 7 unique weapon types<br></li><li>70+ modifiers and 300+ special abilities to mix and match<br></li><li>Build a demon, a humanoid castle, or a blend! Many skins to mix and match, all earned without microtransactions!<br></li><li>Even a fun automatic GIF generator, connected to our Discord, for easy bragging!</li></ul>",
